                  <h3 class="text-center font-bold text-lg mb-4 uppercase tracking-wide">Customer Feedback Consent Form</h3>
                  <p class="mb-4"><strong>Business Name:</strong> ____________________________</p>

                  <p class="font-bold mb-2">Customer Information:</p>
                  <p class="mb-2">Name: ____________________________</p>
                  <p class="mb-2">Phone Number: ____________________________</p>
                  <p class="mb-4">Email (optional): ____________________________</p>

